('94011','32367','5','Luxury residence for sale in Son Vida'),
('94012','32368','5','Son Vida is a beautiful gated luxury residential area, on the outskirts of Palma de Mallorca. In the immediate neighborhood of 3 golf courses and two five star hotels, this dream residence is situated on a large plot 7.345m². From here you have a fantastic panoramic view of Palma de Mallorca and the mountains of Son Vida. This residence is absolutely quiet and leaves nothing to be desired. It offers a total of 2,500m² of living space. About the entrance hall on the ground floor with double height ceiling and gallery, one enters the main house. From here you have access to a salon with fireplace, dining room, kitchen with dining area, library, study, TV room, living room, master bedroom with smaller 2nd bedroom with bathroom en suite, dressing room and a spacious marble bathroom.\r\nIn the basement there is a wine cellar, exercise room, a separate staff apartment with 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 2 kitchen and living room, ironing room, storage room and laundry room.\r\nA Hollywood staircase leads you to the first floor. Here you receive a billiards table in the loft. Further you have 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms en suite, and an office room with fireplace. All rooms have access to terraces.\r\nThe separately located guest house offers a spa area with swimming pool (12x3m), a sauna and a bar, as well as 2 apartments on the 1st floor each one with one bedroom, living room, kitchen and bathroom. The high quality facilities includes,  marble floors. air condition system w / c, under floor heating,  lift, Bose sound system and much more.\r\nIn the park-like outdoor area includes a south facing pool, barbecue area, tennis court, garage for 4 cars and open parking places. \r\nA 3,000m² large sea view nabor plot can be additionally purchased\r\n'),
